---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Services — CA Accounting | Tax, Bookkeeping, CFO Advisory"
  description="Tax planning, outsourced bookkeeping, business incorporation, CFO advisory, and consulting for individuals, small businesses, and growing firms across California."
>
  <!-- Header -->
  <section class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 fade-in">Services</p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-navy leading-tight mb-6 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          The full range of an accounting firm. The focus of a specialist.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-lg leading-relaxed fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
          From a single tax return to fractional CFO leadership, every engagement is staffed by senior professionals and reviewed by a partner. No handoffs to junior staff, no learning curve every spring.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Service nav anchors -->
  <section class="border-b border-line bg-cream py-6 sticky top-[57px] lg:top-[73px] z-40 backdrop-blur-md">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-sm">
        <a href="#tax" class="text-charcoal hover:text-forest font-medium transition-colors">Tax</a>
        <a href="#accounting" class="text-charcoal hover:text-forest font-medium transition-colors">Accounting & Bookkeeping</a>
        <a href="#cfo" class="text-charcoal hover:text-forest font-medium transition-colors">CFO Advisory</a>
        <a href="#small-business" class="text-charcoal hover:text-forest font-medium transition-colors">Small Business</a>
        <a href="#incorporation" class="text-charcoal hover:text-forest font-medium transition-colors">Incorporation</a>
        <a href="#consulting" class="text-charcoal hover:text-forest font-medium transition-colors">Consulting</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tax -->
  <section id="tax" class="py-20 md:py-24 scroll-mt-32">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div class="lg:col-span-1 fade-in">
          <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">01</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-4">Tax & Planning</h2>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
            Tax services led by an Enrolled Agent — the IRS's highest credential for tax practitioners — and structured around year-round planning, not just April scrambles.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Return preparation</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Federal, state, and multi-state returns for individuals, businesses, partnerships, S-corps, and trusts.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Year-round planning</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Quarterly check-ins to surface deduction opportunities, optimize entity structure, and avoid surprises.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">IRS representation</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Audit support, notice response, and direct representation in front of the IRS by an Enrolled Agent.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Estate & trust planning</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Coordination with your attorney to minimize tax exposure on trusts, estates, and gifts.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Retirement strategy</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Contribution planning across SEP-IRA, Solo 401(k), defined benefit, and other vehicles for owners and high earners.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Multi-state filings</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Tour income, residuals, royalties, multi-property holdings — anywhere your work crosses state lines.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Accounting -->
  <section id="accounting" class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-24 scroll-mt-32">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div class="lg:col-span-1 fade-in">
          <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">02</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-4">Accounting & Bookkeeping</h2>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
            Outsourced accounting for owners who want clean books, accurate financials, and someone they can call when a number doesn't look right.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Outsourced bookkeeping</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Monthly reconciliation, transaction coding, and AP/AR — full handoff or hybrid with your in-house team.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Financial statements</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">P&L, balance sheet, and cash flow statements prepared monthly or quarterly to GAAP standards.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Reviews & compilations</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Bank-ready financial reports for loans, investor reporting, or annual confirmations.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Payroll services</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Payroll processing, quarterly filings, year-end W-2s and 1099s, contractor onboarding.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">QuickBooks support</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Setup, cleanup, training, and ongoing maintenance for QuickBooks Online and Desktop.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Cash flow management</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Forecasting and budgeting models so you know what's coming before it gets here.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CFO -->
  <section id="cfo" class="py-20 md:py-24 scroll-mt-32">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div class="lg:col-span-1 fade-in">
          <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">03</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-4">Outsourced CFO & Controller</h2>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
            For businesses that need senior financial leadership but aren't ready for a full-time hire. Scale up or down by month based on what's actually happening in the business.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Strategic financial reporting</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Monthly board-grade reporting, KPI dashboards, and variance analysis you can act on.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Cash flow forecasting</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">13-week and 12-month rolling forecasts so working capital is never a surprise.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">M&A support</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Due diligence, quality of earnings analysis, and post-close integration on either side of a transaction.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Business valuation</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Defensible valuations for buy-sell agreements, succession, gifting, or partner buyouts.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Audits & assurance</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Audit, review, and compilation services where third-party assurance is required.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Banking & loan support</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Loan packaging, lender presentations, and ongoing covenant compliance reporting.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Small business -->
  <section id="small-business" class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-24 scroll-mt-32">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div class="lg:col-span-1 fade-in">
          <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">04</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-4">Small Business</h2>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
            A complete back-office solution for small businesses that don't have an in-house finance team — and don't need to.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Bundled accounting</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Bookkeeping, payroll, sales tax, and annual returns as a single monthly engagement.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Owner advisory</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Quarterly check-ins on profitability, owner compensation, and tax position before year-end.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Sales tax compliance</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Multi-state sales tax registration, filings, and nexus analysis for businesses that sell across state lines.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Banking & lending support</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Help packaging financials for lines of credit, SBA loans, or equipment financing.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Incorporation -->
  <section id="incorporation" class="py-20 md:py-24 scroll-mt-32">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div class="lg:col-span-1 fade-in">
          <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">05</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-4">Business Incorporation</h2>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
            Entity formation done right the first time — with the tax and legal trade-offs explained in plain English before you sign.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Entity selection</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">LLC, S-corp, C-corp, partnership — comparing each for your situation, not selling you the most expensive option.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Formation filings</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Articles of incorporation, EIN application, S-corp election, and state registrations.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Loan-out corporations</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">For working performers and creatives — structured to capture deductions and split income across years.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">New business advisory</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Setting up your books, payroll, and tax accounts so the first year doesn't end in cleanup.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Consulting -->
  <section id="consulting" class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-24 scroll-mt-32">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div class="lg:col-span-1 fade-in">
          <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">06</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-4">Consulting</h2>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
            Project-based engagements for inflection points: a sale, a succession, a turnaround, a major hiring decision.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Succession planning</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Transferring ownership to the next generation, employees, or external buyers in a tax-efficient way.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Debt restructuring</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Renegotiation, consolidation, and refinance support when the current debt structure isn't working.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Business plans</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Financial models and projections for fundraising, lender review, or internal planning.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">College & education planning</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">529 plans, custodial accounts, and tax-aware funding strategies for family education savings.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-navy text-cream py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-cream mb-6">
          Not sure what you need?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-cream/80 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
          That's what the consultation is for. We'll listen to where you are, look at what you've got, and tell you the smallest thing that would make the biggest difference.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="btn-modern inline-block bg-forest text-cream font-semibold px-10 py-4 rounded hover:bg-forest-hover transition-colors"
        >
          Schedule a Free Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
